# model_store/
#
# This directory holds the trained SVM classifier artefacts:
#   svm_classifier.pkl   — scikit-learn Pipeline (Normalizer + SVC)
#   label_map.json       — {int → username} mapping
#
# Both files are written automatically when POST /train is called.
# They are intentionally NOT committed to version control
# (add to .gitignore) because they contain user-specific biometric data.
